{"TopicId":167158,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Serious Scientific Answers to Absurd Hypothetical questions","CreatedByName":"DAL59","CreatedById":180784,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-03T20:21:11Z","PageNum":29,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-22T19:26:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223526985\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022167158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221548185044\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022107381\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Green Baron\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Green Baron said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Romans would of course use their cloaking device.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... err ... no ... wrong movie. Those were the Romulans ... nevermind.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese\u00A0were Romanian cloaking devices.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022d4d1eaa23bad71451c1a7097f8c0f866.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022720\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.pinimg.com/originals/d4/d1/ea/d4d1eaa23bad71451c1a7097f8c0f866.jpg\u0022 width=\u0022540\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-22T19:26:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u00